<title>lw tʿrf ḥby lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- msẖ lạqy ḥḍn dạfy ạ̉jry wạ̉rmy
 ʿlyh ḥmly
 wlạ lạqy ḥb kạfy ymlạ frạgẖy wysẖbʿ qlby
 lw tʿrf ḥby lyk lw sẖft ạlly ạ̉nạ dqth ʿsẖạnk
 ṭryq ạldẖl msẖyt fyh wḥṭyt ạ̉nạ nfsy bdạlk
 ạlqrạr- ʿsẖạn ạ̹nt ʿlyã gẖạly wmkạnk fy qlby
 ʿạly
 tʿạla fy ḥḍny qrby dạ ạ̉nạ msẖtạq llqạk
 2- ạ̉nạ ʿsẖt ḥyạty lṣạḥb wtʿbt mn jrḥh ly
 ḥty̱ fy tʿby mạ lqyth wlạ ḥn wlạ fkr fy
 lw sẖft ạ̹zạy ṣlbwny ʿly̱ kẖsẖbẗ wsẖdwạ ạ̹ydy
 ḥty̱ fy ʿṭsẖy mạ rwwny wmạḥdsẖ kạn ḥạss by</lyrics>
</song>